{
  "name": "Open-Nav (Habitat VLN-CE)",
  "kind": "graph",
  "description": "Faithful AgentCanvas port of [Open-Nav](https://arxiv.org/abs/2409.18794) (Qiao et al., ICRA 2025). Spatial-temporal chain-of-thought VLN-CE pipeline: Stage 1 instruction parse (action + landmark detection, once per episode), Stage 2 progress estimation, Stage 3 ensemble decision (3 navigator samples → fusion → tie-break → random fallback). Uses env_habitat for the simulator, opennav_waypoint for the frozen TRM_net + image encoders, opennav_perception for RAM tagging + SpatialBot depth-aware captions, and the opennav method nodeset for prompts/parsers/decision logic. Step cap is 6 or 8 depending on parsed action count, mirroring base_il_trainer_llm.py:394.",
